<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Santix Windrider <br>
46 Ranger <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ublakkon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>blakkon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 366<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/12/02 11:33:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2140.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> FV is a server full of twinks...</span><hr size=1> The fact that most people dont have an alt means things get sold very cheaply just to get rid of them.  The attentive player can easily have gear far above their level at 20..... <p>Lorec <br>
Wandering Judge of the Tribunal <br>


